{"tid":2395451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"形容中國是美國最危險對手　拜登：但若有利隨時準備合作","createTime":"2021-02-05T02:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T09:23:17.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"be8348e1ee5d944670dfa23e23737c89db54aa4a","tid":2395451,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:00:49.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n美國總統拜登周四發表上任以來首場主要外交政策演說，形容中國是美國最危險的競爭對手，但又表示若符合利益，美國願與中國合作。<br />\n<br />\n拜登說：「我們將...直截了當地接受最危險的競爭對手中國對我們的繁榮、安全和民主價值的挑戰....我們將對抗中國的經濟陋習、反擊其好鬥行為、抵擋中國對人權、知識產權和全球管治的攻擊...但當符合美國利益時，我們準備好與北京合作。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210205/VKDHWYVYTRCKNCRQJAVLHM5VO4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210205%2FVKDHWYVYTRCKNCRQJAVLHM5VO4%2F&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9EXO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=1874c30a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210205%2FVKDHWYVYTRCKNCRQJAVLHM5VO4%2F&h=5794b10a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210205/VKDHWYVYTRCKNCRQJAVLHM5VO4/</a>"},{"pid":"beac730266de9295432a390e058bd2d64fec9811","tid":2395451,"uid":340088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"Chinese dog"},{"pid":"2ce4362f773fb761ff22a49b3086142b68300efe","tid":2395451,"uid":178187,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:04:01.000Z","msg":"凖備進入黑暗時代啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8cb71b74f50bd776abf2d66daf43570940ddfb5","tid":2395451,"uid":256837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:04:35.000Z","msg":"好多美國企業咪一樣用新疆血汗工廠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d364725ce9813eb260e80e205bddc7521b62b3d1","tid":2395451,"uid":226955,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"咁予盾嘅說話都講得出，白登智商有冇60